def_cn: 双鱼宫，双鱼座（黄道十二宫之一；出生于2月19日至3月20日之间的人属此星座）
def_en: Pisces is one of the twelve signs of the zodiac. Its symbol is two fish. People who are born approximately between the 19th of February and the 20th of March come under this sign.

def_cn: 出生于双鱼宫时段的人
def_en: A Pisces is a person whose sign of the zodiac is Pisces.
